
Help

dotnet -h
dotnet new -h
dotnet sln -h

----------------
Project creation
----------------
Create solution:
dotnet new solution --name ExerciseDomain
Create console project:
dotnet new console --name ExerciseDomain.ConsoleApp

Class Library
dotnet new classlib --name ExerciseDomain.Shared

Unit Test (xUnit)
dotnet new xunit -o ExerciseDomain.Tests
dotnet add package Moq --version 4.14.3

Add project to solution:
dotnet sln add ./ExerciseDomain.ConsoleApp/ExerciseDomain.ConsoleApp.csproj
dotnet sln add ./ExerciseDomain.Tests/ExerciseDomain.Tests.csproj
CodingExercise.ConsoleApp

------------
Build & Run
------------
dotnet build
cd ExerciseDomain.ConsoleApp
dotnet run
